reviewText:
I bought this circa 2006, directly as a manufacture-to-order DVD from Indixflix, when Indieflix was a Seattle International Film Sponsor.

I haven't seen the film in years, but it was worth quite a few lowbrow laughs. As the description suggests, it's full of fart humor. Besides the fart humor, it's also a solid parody of the film noir genre. It was shot in Seattle.
